@node "Updates" "Where to get Updates"
 
 @{b}WHERE TO GETS THE UPDATES@{ub}
 
 @{b}WAY #1 MAILORDER@{ub} - (the slow way)

 Send @{"me" link "Register" 0} a empty disk and an envelope with an unused stamp, and I`ll put
 all new versions on the disk and will send them back within latest 1 Week.
 
 @{b}WAY #2 DISTRIBUTION SITE@{ub} - (the fast way)
 
 Call one of our @{"distributionásites" link "Innovation" 0} to register your updates.
@endnode

